Package: firomax
Type: Package
Title: Forecast Informed Reservoir Operations for MAXimum hydroelectric power sales
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sean Turner
Maintainer: Sean Turner <sean.turner@pnnl.gov>
Description: firomax performs Dynamic Programming to optimize within week reservoir releases for maximum hydropower revenue.
    Weekly release targets from the `ISTARF-CONUS` dataset may be used to soft-constrain operations.
    Sub-daily release decisions are optimized in full-week or rolling-horizon mode for given deterministic price and streamflow forecasts.
